name: Adventure of the Super Fly-ing Tiny Wing-s Birds Run - Free Kids Racing Game
name_original: Adventure of the Super Fly-ing Tiny Wing-s Birds Run - Free Kids Racing Game
description:
Hang on tight because you've been invited on an adventure with the Super Tiny Wing Birds! Enjoy this fast paced racing action game with these high flying birds!

Features:
-6 cool, unique birds to choose from!
-Nextpeer Multiplayer capabilities to play against friends!
-High-def quality graphics and amazing music!
-GameCenter enabled to check your rankings against other players!
-Many different levels to unlock and beat!
